OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779289870
OL,3,CLarge tree dumped in middle of road in
OL,4,C'serious fly-tipping incident'
OL,6,FA council is appealing for more
OL,7,Finformation after a large tree was
OL,8,Fdumped in the middle of a road in what
OL,9,Fthey believe is a "serious" case of
OL,10,Ffly-tipping.
OL,12,FHarborough District Council, in
OL,13,FLeicestershire council, said it dealt
OL,14,Fwith the incident in Ullesthorpe Road
OL,15,Fnear Ashby Parva on 15 May.
OL,17,FThe council said the incident involved
OL,18,Fthe illegal dumping of a large tree
OL,19,Fand other household waste, which
OL,20,Fresulted in the road being blocked.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
