PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779289870
OL,3,CLarge tree dumped in middle of road in
OL,4,C'serious fly-tipping incident'
OL,6,FThey say they would like to hear from
OL,7,Fanyone in the area who saw anything
OL,8,Fsuspicious or a vehicle carrying a
OL,9,Flarge tree.
OL,11,FDavid Page, cabinet lead for
OL,12,FNeighbourhood Services said, "The
OL,13,Fdumped material obstructed the
OL,14,Fhighway, creating a danger to road
OL,15,Fusers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779289870
OL,3,CLarge tree dumped in middle of road in
OL,4,C'serious fly-tipping incident'
OL,6,F"Fly-tipping, obstructing the highway
OL,7,Fand creating hazardous conditions for
OL,8,Fothers are serious matters and may
OL,9,Famount to criminal offences. This was
OL,10,Fdangerous, deeply disrespectful to
OL,11,Fresidents and exactly the kind of
OL,12,Fillegal behaviour we will not tolerate.
OL,14,F"Our teams acted quickly to make the
OL,15,Farea safe and clear the waste.
OL,16,FResidents will pay for this clean-up
OL,17,Fthrough their council tax, but those
OL,18,Fresponsible should be in no doubt, we
OL,19,Fintend to make them pay for what they
OL,20,Fhave done.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779289870
OL,3,CLarge tree dumped in middle of road in
OL,4,C'serious fly-tipping incident'
OL,6,F"Harborough will not tolerate this
OL,7,Fbehaviour. Let me be really clear, we
OL,8,Fhave a zero-tolerance approach to fly-
OL,9,Ftipping and illegal waste dumping. We
OL,10,Fwill work with partner agencies and do
OL,11,Feverything possible to identify and
OL,12,Fpursue those responsible."
